# Formatting

This project uses Prettier for code formatting. Match these settings in all generated code:

- 4-space indentation (no tabs)
- Single quotes for strings
- Semicolons at end of statements
- Trailing commas everywhere (ES5+)
- 100 character line width
- Spaces inside object braces: `{ foo }` not `{foo}`

After making changes, run `yarn format` to normalize formatting.
